WEBVTT

00:00:02.948 --> 00:00:06.688
TAPE NUMBER FIVE INTERVIEW WITH MR KALMAN SHLOMOVICH.

00:00:07.335 --> 00:00:10.603
ir hot geredt vegn ayer

00:00:11.638 --> 00:00:15.243
redn mit dem d- mit dem Sho-

00:00:13.326 --> 00:00:14.940
Shulye.

00:00:15.317 --> 00:00:16.998
dem Shulye Mihayli.

00:00:16.110 --> 00:00:17.083
Shulye.

00:00:18.152 --> 00:00:20.778
azoy ven undz ho'mir geredt tsuzamen,

00:00:21.375 --> 00:00:24.322
unter fir oygn, zogt, hot er mir gezogt,

00:00:25.273 --> 00:00:27.140
"tomer du vilst blaybn do,

00:00:27.754 --> 00:00:29.469
demolts gib ikh dir es tsurik.

00:00:30.555 --> 00:00:32.822
ober du vilst forn avek

00:00:32.822 --> 00:00:37.856
ikh veys yi- keyner iz nishto, yeder du bist nor eyner geblibn nokh mit dem Volvn,"

00:00:39.786 --> 00:00:45.719
SO di mame hot gevolt ikh zol blaybn far mir, far vos zol zolstu veln, hob ikh im gezogt

00:00:46.266 --> 00:00:47.728
vegn mayn bruder,

00:00:48.932 --> 00:00:51.001
ober er hot mir nisht gevolt dos tsurikgebn.

00:00:51.396 --> 00:00:53.364
hob ikh im gegebn in protses arayn.

00:00:54.889 --> 00:00:56.598
ikh hob im gegebn in protses arayn,

00:00:56.598 --> 00:01:00.114
ober in der tsayt ze'mir geven zeyer,

00:01:01.200 --> 00:01:08.028
er iz gevezn a zitser bay der bay der protsesn, iz er gevezn, er hot zikh gehat shoyn oyf gearbet

00:01:09.267 --> 00:01:13.361
bay di in tsayt fun Rusnland, in Ukraine.

00:01:15.207 --> 00:01:18.777
iz er, hob ikh im gegebn protses arayn, un

00:01:18.852 --> 00:01:20.685
protses hot mir geurteylt

00:01:20.978 --> 00:01:24.982
az ikh ken hobn a zekste, a tsvelefte teyl

00:01:24.982 --> 00:01:26.590
funem funem farmegn.

00:01:28.808 --> 00:01:34.607
zog ikh farn farn JUDGE, vos vos epes?

00:01:35.642 --> 00:01:37.964
zogt er, "azoy iz der deys.

00:01:38.494 --> 00:01:44.102
deys vos dayn tate, helft geher,

00:01:44.102 --> 00:01:48.984
deys hot di mame gehat a rekht tsu tsugebn, vayl zi iz gevezn der der yoyresh.

00:01:49.547 --> 00:01:52.561
dem hostu gornisht, vayl zi iz s'ir farlir.

00:01:53.192 --> 00:01:55.582
fun dem iberike zakhn,

00:01:56.145 --> 00:01:59.767
bistu geblibn eyner aleyn, kenstu bakumen a tsvelefte teyl."

00:02:00.617 --> 00:02:03.058
zeyer ongehoybn tsu veynen, farfirn,

00:02:03.520 --> 00:02:05.792
hobn klapn aroysgefirt mikh un fartik.

00:02:07.333 --> 00:02:10.482
bin ikh gegangen nokh es apelirt oyf Ungvar, Uzhgorod.

00:02:12.362 --> 00:02:17.284
Uzhgorod hot tsurikgevizn az m'zol makhn a nayem protses.

00:02:19.500 --> 00:02:26.835
in der tsayt iz gevezn zenen aheymgekumen shoyn di fun der tshekhisher legyoner.

00:02:27.313 --> 00:02:32.943
iz gevezn eyner an oremer mentsh, vos er iz gevezn, er iz gevorn

00:02:34.027 --> 00:02:36.876
der meyor fun funem dorf,

00:02:39.008 --> 00:02:42.241
un er iz geven zeyer a gegner.

00:02:43.193 --> 00:02:45.864
der, zogt er, zenen gezesn in der heym, ikh bin gegangen

00:02:45.864 --> 00:02:48.249
dinen dos militer, un ikh hob deys?

00:02:48.289 --> 00:02:51.517
un der hot zikh azoy ongelebt, aza farmegn tsugenumen,

00:02:51.517 --> 00:02:53.699
yeder hot dokh gevust, dos gantse dorf

00:02:53.925 --> 00:02:57.581
az m'fort avek, m'hot avekgenumen di ale zakhn.

00:02:57.807 --> 00:03:01.361
m'hot dokh mit deys ver iz gegangen farkoyfn, oyf vos aroyf, far vemen?

00:03:03.156 --> 00:03:05.225
un s'geven ayngeshribn tsen yor.

00:03:07.459 --> 00:03:11.453
zogt er, "Kalmen, du broykhst nisht geyn tsu keyn protses.

00:03:12.387 --> 00:03:14.642
ikh vel mit dir makhn a kurts protses."

00:03:15.778 --> 00:03:22.285
er iz gegangen, er hot tsunam gerufn di zitsers funem fun der fun dem dorf, vos zenen gevezn in der oysgevelter,

00:03:22.883 --> 00:03:24.412
un m'hot im gelozt rufn.

00:03:27.945 --> 00:03:31.601
fregt er im tsu ersht deys, "far vos hostu ibergeshribn deys?

00:03:31.624 --> 00:03:35.434
s'dokh nisht gevezn nor zeks zeks un fertsiker yor?

00:03:35.434 --> 00:03:39.262
du host dos UNK, biz eyn un fuftsiker hostu nisht getort dos ibershraybn."

00:03:40.045 --> 00:03:46.924
yo, ikh hob gevust, zogt er, az zey zenen nishto keyner, hob ikh es vos deys, hot er ibergeshribn.

00:03:49.258 --> 00:03:52.053
SO du host batsolt, zogt er, azoy fil gelt

00:03:53.005 --> 00:03:57.150
a far far aza farmegn, vi hostu gekent koyfn aza hoyz

00:03:57.493 --> 00:04:04.304
mit aza gortn? s'geven a fun a gantse gas iz gevezn a gortn fun undzere, fun eyn hoy- gas tsu der anderer iz undz gevezn.

00:04:08.800 --> 00:04:12.000
un di ale zakhn, undz hobn gehat a a halbe mil,

00:04:12.124 --> 00:04:13.698
gehat di polonines,

00:04:13.698 --> 00:04:16.083
ales s'geven ariber far im.

00:04:17.997 --> 00:04:20.980
SO, bistu, zogt er, mentshn hobn ge- ge- geblutert

00:04:20.980 --> 00:04:24.150
un zey hobn gedeys un du host gevorn a kulkul?

00:04:24.291 --> 00:04:25.584
du host dikh, zogt er,

00:04:26.468 --> 00:04:30.123
ho'mir far dir eyn plats, shrayb deys,

00:04:31.530 --> 00:04:33.650
m'darf im aroysshikn als kulkul,

00:04:33.792 --> 00:04:35.811
m'darf dir avekshikn oyf Sibir.

00:04:36.627 --> 00:04:37.847
az er hot gekent,

00:04:37.847 --> 00:04:44.687
iz er dokh nisht geven keyn proster mentsh, er iz gevezn, zogt er, er hot gehat gelt un er hot zikh ongelebt in der tsaytn ven mentshn hobn gegebn dos,

00:04:46.195 --> 00:04:48.467
ven er hot gehert di reyd,

00:04:48.473 --> 00:04:50.593
iz er oyfgeshtanen, zogt er, ikh gib im tsurik.

00:04:53.248 --> 00:04:56.583
shrayb zikh unter, hot ongeshribn az er

00:04:56.893 --> 00:05:01.612
er get zikh unter, er get tsurik ales, dos gantse farmegn mir.

00:05:03.289 --> 00:05:06.101
un azoy iz er a- aroysgegangen,

00:05:06.613 --> 00:05:09.374
zogt, zest, ikh hob mit im gemakht a kurtsn,

00:05:11.220 --> 00:05:13.374
du vilst dem, vilst dos farmegn

00:05:13.498 --> 00:05:17.036
SO blaybstu mit dem farmegn un geyst oyf oyf Sibir.

00:05:18.696 --> 00:05:24.579
azoy vos undz ze'mir azoy tsugangen zikh,

00:05:25.007 --> 00:05:26.486
mer ho'mir nisht geredt

00:05:26.661 --> 00:05:28.359
mit im, keyn mol nisht.

00:05:29.749 --> 00:05:32.966
gelegn zikh azoy k- tsuzamen kumen, ikh hob nokh gevoynt dort,

00:05:33.563 --> 00:05:36.662
un fleg er ge- avekgeyn der anderer zayt,

00:05:36.820 --> 00:05:41.438
vos hot ir geton in in Kolotshove der gantse tsayt?

00:05:42.017 --> 00:05:44.356
ikh hob gearbet in a STORE,

00:05:45.223 --> 00:05:47.140
baym Ors velkher hot,

00:05:48.042 --> 00:05:51.529
befor iz gevezn in kolkhoz

00:05:51.687 --> 00:05:53.295
hot men gemostn di

00:05:53.295 --> 00:05:57.620
far di mentshn, m'hot tsugenumen di shtiber, di hay- di gertner,

00:05:57.829 --> 00:05:59.648
hot men mikh oysgeklibn

00:05:59.648 --> 00:06:04.167
az ikh zol oysmestn nokh mit m- nokh a erminer firer,

00:06:04.630 --> 00:06:07.897
vifl er meg hobn bay di shtub, vifl s'geher im,

00:06:08.005 --> 00:06:10.429
azoy funem kolkhoz hot men mir gegebn

00:06:10.958 --> 00:06:14.186
ale produktn, ales vos ikh hob gedarft hobn tsu lebn.

00:06:14.186 --> 00:06:15.929
nokh dem hob ikh gearbet in STORE.

00:06:17.455 --> 00:06:24.317
ikh hob gehat a STORE vos hot ge- s'gege- gehat ales vos iz gevezn far arbayter, dos iz geven bay undz in hoyz taken.

00:06:27.073 --> 00:06:29.851
iz geven der STORE, deys hot gehert farn Ors,

00:06:30.263 --> 00:06:31.860
vos hot gegebn

00:06:32.372 --> 00:06:36.922
far mentshn. s'dokh in di STORE nisht gevezn keyn tsuker, keyn gornisht iz nisht gevezn.

00:06:37.435 --> 00:06:39.769
SO far di arbayter velkhe zey hobn gearbet

00:06:39.769 --> 00:06:42.238
in bay baym vald,

00:06:42.717 --> 00:06:49.596
dey hobn bakumen tengere, dey hobn bakumen vayts, un dey hobn bakumen kashes, dey hobn bakumen ale meln,

00:06:49.855 --> 00:06:53.746
oykhet loyt vifl s'iz tsugeteylt. un tsuker.

00:06:54.529 --> 00:06:57.071
SO ikh hob gehat dem STORE,

00:06:57.195 --> 00:07:00.007
vos far a regirung iz dos geven?

00:06:59.018 --> 00:07:04.344
dos iz gevezn bay di ukrainer shoyn, bay U.S.R.

00:07:04.367 --> 00:07:06.212
U.S.S. dos iz shoyn geven

00:07:06.212 --> 00:07:08.647
r- s'sh- geven unter Rusland?

00:07:06.578 --> 00:07:08.465
yo, ven ikh bin gekumen tsu-

00:07:08.465 --> 00:07:14.823
yo, ven ikh bin gekumen tsurik iz dokh shoyn gevezn Rusland dort. SO,

00:07:13.750 --> 00:07:18.452
Kolotsh- Kolotshove iz ge- gevorn U.S.S.R.

00:07:15.538 --> 00:07:17.543
Kolotshave iz gevorn

00:07:17.543 --> 00:07:23.362
U.S.S.R. o- ober dos hot geheysn Ukraine azoy vi haynt s'iz s'nor s'hot gehert tsu U.S.S.R.

00:07:24.010 --> 00:07:29.404
SO far di arbayter iz gevezn di ershte, far m- andere mentshn hot men zikh nisht gezorgt ober di arbe-

00:07:29.460 --> 00:07:31.091
SO di ale zakhn

00:07:31.806 --> 00:07:35.815
biz vant, nisht mer gedakht, ikh hob khasene gehat,

00:07:36.582 --> 00:07:40.153
hob ikh gearbet in dem STORE biz fuftsiker yor fun,

00:07:40.210 --> 00:07:43.629
vos far a yidishe lebn iz geven in

00:07:43.703 --> 00:07:46.650
Kolotshove di fi- di finf yor?

00:07:47.584 --> 00:07:50.902
keyn yidish lebn iz nisht gevezn, ober s'gevezn a dorf

00:07:50.908 --> 00:07:57.348
Negrevits, nisht vayt, s'hot oykh geheysn Kolotshave nor s'geven a teyl fun dem, Negrevits.

00:07:58.080 --> 00:07:59.947
in dem Negrevits hobn gevoynt

00:08:00.966 --> 00:08:07.474
nokh di shlakht a ikh meyn a draysik mishpokhes.

00:08:07.311 --> 00:08:08.216
yidishe?

00:08:07.952 --> 00:08:08.958
yidishe.

00:08:09.420 --> 00:08:11.540
SO oyf di yontoyvim

00:08:11.597 --> 00:08:15.118
ober yortsayt, oyf y- oyf yontev,

00:08:15.462 --> 00:08:17.121
fleg ikh arayngeyn ahin.

00:08:17.121 --> 00:08:21.919
ikh fleg arayn shpatsirn in der fri ahin. dos iz nisht geven vayt, geven a in gantsn a por kilometer.

00:08:21.756 --> 00:08:24.416
un religyezer lebn vos iz dos geven?

00:08:23.477 --> 00:08:28.972
yo, religyezer lebn. dort s'geven, m- m'hot gehat dort a shoykhet, s'gevezn di.

00:08:30.328 --> 00:08:39.890
un shpeter, di ale mentshn zenen fun dort avekgegangen oyf Khust, voynen.

00:08:39.794 --> 00:08:40.834
far vos?

00:08:41.517 --> 00:08:42.686
far dem vayl

00:08:42.686 --> 00:08:51.112
m'hot nisht gevolt zayn, do iz der shokhtim zenen avekgeforn, s'nisht gevezn nor eyn shoykhet, der iz avekgeforn oyf Khust, s'nisht geven keyn kosher dey.

00:08:51.135 --> 00:08:57.119
SO in Khust iz gevezn dray shokhtim, s'gevezn a shul, s'gevezn a dey, SO iz men gegangen,

00:08:57.295 --> 00:08:59.181
iz men aribergegangen voynen.

00:08:59.181 --> 00:09:00.714
ikh hob khasene gehat,

00:09:00.670 --> 00:09:05.726
vu hot ir khasene gehat? un v- vi azoy hot ir zikh getrofn mit ayer froy?

00:09:02.053 --> 00:09:03.042
Khust.

00:09:05.749 --> 00:09:11.548
ikh hob mir getrofn, ikh hob gehat a geshvesterkind, Feyge,

00:09:12.263 --> 00:09:15.626
zi hot gevoynt in Khust.

00:09:15.626 --> 00:09:17.943
oykhet iz aribergekumen fun Senever,

00:09:18.000 --> 00:09:22.803
iz aribergekumen voynen, ales iz aribergekumen, fun ale deys, fun ale derfer, iz aribergekumen oyf Khust voynen.

00:09:24.902 --> 00:09:30.110
un mayn vayb hot demolts gearbet in a bufet.

00:09:30.842 --> 00:09:36.067
zi hot gehat oystrinken mit farshidene zakhn tsu farbaysn, tsigretlekh,

00:09:37.305 --> 00:09:44.961
SO ikh hob oykh gearbet in a dem in zelbn deys, nor deys hot gehert tsu Khust, yents gehert tsu Bushtane.

00:09:46.468 --> 00:09:49.055
bin ikh arayngegangen alts, s'geven a meydl dort,

00:09:49.055 --> 00:09:50.935
bin ikh arayngegangen zi redn mit ir.

00:09:51.042 --> 00:09:54.827
SO geyt men arayn m'zol redn mit eyne, bin ikh gegangen oykh koyfn tsigaretn.

00:09:54.827 --> 00:09:56.165
ikh hob keyn mol nisht gereykhert.

00:09:57.235 --> 00:10:01.667
ober ikh hob gekoyft tsigaretn un ikh hob dey alts bin ikh arayngegangen.

00:10:02.719 --> 00:10:10.290
un azoy vos undz ho'mir geshmuest mit undzer k- mayn kuzin,

00:10:10.701 --> 00:10:17.883
zogt zi, "efsher vestu gevolt khasene mit der mit dey meydl?"

00:10:19.476 --> 00:10:24.903
ikh veys nisht yo vayl ikh veys zi hot shoyn a zi geyt arum mit a yingl un deys,

00:10:25.163 --> 00:10:28.262
zogt er, "deys zorg dikh nisht, az du vilst

00:10:28.352 --> 00:10:29.848
vel ikh shmuesn mit ir."

00:10:32.487 --> 00:10:38.117
zogt, du veyst du kenst dokh dos meydl, yo, e- zi ken mikh oykhet, ikh ken zi oykhet un,

00:10:38.764 --> 00:10:44.107
s'gevezn in a oyf rosheshone, zogt er, "kum ariber tsu mir oyf rosheshone oyf Khust."

00:10:45.075 --> 00:10:47.853
ikh bin dokh mimeyle oyf rosheshone iz er dokh gekumen oyf Khust,

00:10:49.530 --> 00:10:51.768
iz eb ikh dir shmuesn mit ir tatn,

00:10:53.260 --> 00:10:56.999
az ikh kum ariber nokhn nokhn esn kum ikh ariber ahin.

00:10:58.812 --> 00:11:05.809
ikh bin gekumen ahin, un un gekent ho'mir zikh dokh, farshteyst, SO ikh zi hot ikh bin geven in droysn, azoy er hot mikh gevart, azoy ikh gedenk,

00:11:06.726 --> 00:11:08.593
er zogt, du vartst mikh mit a shtekn.

00:11:10.303 --> 00:11:16.540
zogt er, a far eynem fun mayn bruder iz dos hitl aropgefaln di deys gey gey ikh aropnemen.

00:11:17.762 --> 00:11:21.688
SO ikh hob mit ir durkhgeshmuest, zog ikh azoy di, zogt zi

00:11:24.934 --> 00:11:29.369
"du kumst arayn, kum arayn dentsmol nisht nor ven du vilst tsigaretn reykhenen,

00:11:29.369 --> 00:11:31.812
ven du UNK meg kenen kum arayn azoy oykhet.

00:11:32.325 --> 00:11:36.262
azoy vos undz ze'mir durkhgegangen a por mol,

00:11:36.262 --> 00:11:42.512
gevust hob ikh ver zi iz un vos zi iz un deys un un ge- i- ikh hob ir gekent befor mit a yor tsayt.

00:11:44.509 --> 00:11:46.308
un ikh hob gezogt, OK ikh

00:11:47.142 --> 00:11:48.935
s'ke- mir ken'mir shmuesn.

00:11:48.935 --> 00:11:50.999
ikh meyn az yo.

00:11:54.060 --> 00:11:55.674
zi flegt mir vos UNK,

00:11:56.338 --> 00:11:58.441
vos vi dakht zikh dir?

00:11:58.448 --> 00:12:02.187
zog ikh, ikh meyn azoy ikh ze az zi iz,

00:12:02.869 --> 00:12:05.158
az ikh vel zogn az yo vil zi oykhet.

00:12:06.177 --> 00:12:09.321
un m'hot mit ir geredt un zi hot oykh gez- tomer,

00:12:09.321 --> 00:12:12.313
ikh meyn az az s'geyt geyn der,

00:12:12.505 --> 00:12:20.649
ir tate iz zeyer bin ikh gefeln geven, er iz geven zeyer aza yidisher mentsh, er hot gezen az ikh

00:12:21.837 --> 00:12:24.143
ikh veys ales un ikh ken ales, kh-

00:12:24.317 --> 00:12:28.597
afile ikh hob nisht gehaltn in der tsayt far dem vayl

00:12:28.975 --> 00:12:31.258
s'nisht geven dort dey,

00:12:31.258 --> 00:12:35.077
ober ikh hob gemuzt arbetn um shabes un ales,

00:12:35.843 --> 00:12:39.566
ober er hot gevolt az ikh zol zayn zayn eydem.

00:12:42.576 --> 00:12:51.210
deroyf bin ikh gekumen tsurik oyf oyf sukes,

00:12:52.110 --> 00:12:57.099
un simkhes toyre iz geven der tnoim.

00:12:57.865 --> 00:13:01.301
ir hot gehat a religyeze khasene?

00:13:00.582 --> 00:13:01.335
yo.

00:13:03.028 --> 00:13:05.705
a REGULAR khasene geven, mit a khupe ales.

00:13:06.117 --> 00:13:11.359
ikh hob haynt nokh di di di ksube mitn mit der tnoim ales.

00:13:11.989 --> 00:13:15.392
vi azoy iz geven di yidishe lebn in Khust?

00:13:16.140 --> 00:13:20.623
Khust iz gevezn a a in der tsayt iz geven zeyer sheyn.

00:13:21.270 --> 00:13:25.651
gehat a shul, hobn gehat di kh- yidishe

00:13:25.675 --> 00:13:29.685
deye shokhtim un nisht yidishe shokhtim, ay- azelkhe

00:13:31.513 --> 00:13:33.684
der ortodoksishe shokhtim,

00:13:34.804 --> 00:13:39.540
gehat mentshn sheyne vos zey hobn gedavnt, der shoykhet hot sheyn gedavnt, s'gevezn azoy

00:13:40.069 --> 00:13:41.750
mentshn ze'mir gegangen

00:13:41.993 --> 00:13:46.847
shabes arbetn, ober koydem in der fri zenen gegangen in shul arayn un der nokh dem gegangen oyf der arbet.

00:13:46.735 --> 00:13:48.669
vos far a arbet hot ir geton?

00:13:48.793 --> 00:13:50.997
ikh hob gearbet in a

00:13:51.274 --> 00:13:55.908
fun dort bin ikh avekgegangen hob ikh gearbet in Arkil Keramik,

00:13:56.893 --> 00:14:00.279
Ayzn Arkil, Khurshova koydem, nokh dem hot es geheysn Arkil Keramik.

00:14:00.403 --> 00:14:02.962
dos iz gevezn in a

00:14:02.968 --> 00:14:07.631
WAREHOUSE hob ikh gearbet. ikh hob aroysgegebn far di gevelber, far

00:14:07.631 --> 00:14:09.527
far, undz ho'mir gehat azoy

00:14:09.921 --> 00:14:12.466
shnayders, shusters,

00:14:12.466 --> 00:14:14.555
far dey ale hot men gegebn skhoyres,

00:14:14.697 --> 00:14:22.132
un m'hot gemakht bershtlekh, der rayb-bershtlekh, farshidene kalekh-bershtlekh.

