shikn zey vu du muzt geyn arbetn.

00:18:36.613 --> 00:18:38.767
fun dem vos zey shikn arbetn

00:18:38.773 --> 00:18:42.255
iz geven a sakh vos hobn genumen nebekh nisht yidishe meydlekh,

00:18:42.255 --> 00:18:43.965
vayl m'hot avekgeshikt arbetn

00:18:43.971 --> 00:18:48.454
doktoyrim mit inzhenirn oyf der velt, un dort hobn zikh farlibt un deys.

00:18:49.185 --> 00:18:51.457
ikh hob moyre gehat tsu dem tsu kumen,

