00:19:31.018 --> 00:19:34.117
SO hob ikh im genumen tsun undz aheym,

00:19:34.157 --> 00:19:36.868
er hot gearbet bayn undz oyf der, in der tsayt

00:19:37.009 --> 00:19:38.403
