00:19:54.947 --> 00:20:01.100
m'hot gehat in Volove hot gehert tsu undz, Selish hot gehert tsu undz,

00:20:01.478 --> 00:20:06.703
Khust di tsvey fabrikn, un Tetsh.

00:20:08.127 --> 00:20:09.673
SO mayn zun

00:20:10.287 --> 00:20:14.010
hot er avekgeshikt eyner fun dey fabrikn, oyf Tetsh, arbetn.

00:20:14.218 --> 00:20:16.620
dort iz er iz er gegangen arbetn.

00:20:16.620 --> 00:20:18.330
koydem hot er gearbet bay undz,

00:20:18.775 --> 00:20:26.312
un azoy oyf der khasene, un zey hobn getantst,

00:20:26.368 --> 00:20:28.488
hob ikh derzen dos meydl,

00:20:29.963 --> 00:20:32.685
er hot tsugebrengt deys meydl vos zi hot genumen,

00:20:32.685 --> 00:20:33.939
hot er tsugebrengt tsu mir.

00:20:34.992 --> 00:20:37.865
mir iz zi zeyer gefeln gevezn, gevorn,

00:20:37.865 --> 00:20:39.912
un ikh zog ir a, zog ikh im,

00:20:39.953 --> 00:20:42.304
oykh er iz nokh geven a yung yingl,

00:20:42.304 --> 00:20:45.313
