zog ver bistu?

00:20:49.032 --> 00:20:51.371
zogt zi, zogt zi mir ver es iz.

00:20:52.373 --> 00:20:57.598
un ven m'hot mir tsugevizn tsu ver zi iz, ikh hob keyn mol nisht gezen di ale yorn.

00:20:57.739 --> 00:21:01.597
un mit zayn mame bin ikh geven bakont,

00:21:02.025 --> 00:21:03.301
ikh hob zi gekent,

00:21:03.392 --> 00:21:06.761
fleg'mir geyn nokh f- in eynem ge- oyf khasenes getantst,

00:21:08.505 --> 00:21:15.080
un azoy hot zikh es ongehoybn deys, zi iz avek lernen zikh nokh in oyf Lemberg, ober zey hobn shoyn gehaltn kontakt, un zey hobn

00:21:17.533 --> 00:21:23.299
un azoy iz gekumen der tsayt vos m'darf avek, m'darf forn oyf Amerike.

