00:22:07.686 --> 00:22:09.502
eyn zakh ken ikh dir zogn,

00:22:10.048 --> 00:22:11.898
tomer du vilst deys meydl,

00:22:13.187 --> 00:22:18.142
nor keyn fardreyen keyn kop nisht, vayl undz darf'mir vorn avek. undz hobn shriftn oyf dir.

00:22:18.823 --> 00:22:21.838
tomer yo, zog mir yo o nisht.

00:22:22.114 --> 00:22:26.954
tomer nisht, zolstu mer mit ir zikh nisht trefn.

00:22:26.954 --> 00:22:30.849
