hot zi nisht geshikt gornisht.

00:27:38.129 --> 00:27:41.687
zi hot zi hot mer nisht geentfert, az undz kumen un dem.

00:27:42.283 --> 00:27:46.597
SO undz ze'mir gekumen, hot men undz der Rav-Tov opgevart oyfn aeroport,

00:27:47.346 --> 00:27:50.242
un er hot undz gebrengt oyf Vilyamsburg.

00:27:51.750 --> 00:27:55.271
un m'hot undz arayngeleygt in a kvatir in U-STREET.

00:27:56.847 --> 00:28:04.063
gevezn nokhn yontev, iz es gevezn JULY der fiftn, pinktlekh iz, hot men nisht gearbet, dos iz geven a fraytik,

00:28:04.120 --> 00:28:09.632
ze'mir ongekumen, s'gevezn a heyser tog,

00:28:10.212 --> 00:28:13.564
vi azoy ze'mir aroysgegangen funem funem fun der kar,

00:28:14.211 --> 00:28:18.744
nisht geforn, nor gegangen, dos iz, azoy s'geven groyser trafik,

00:28:18.936 --> 00:28:22.355
m'hot undz, ze'mir ze'mir ongekumen a por sho far lekht-tsindn.

00:28:23.138 --> 00:28:30.574
s'gevezn ongeport lekht, TISSUES, azelkhe zakhn. a sider.

00:28:32.908 --> 00:28:35.808
zogt er dort der vos er hot undz gebrengt,

00:28:35.808 --> 00:28:39.146
"ir't kumen tsu mayn tatn oyf shabes."

00:28:40.198 --> 00:28:41.508
zog ikh, "antshuldiks mir.

00:28:42.392 --> 00:28:45.221
ikh gey nisht tsu keynem nisht, ikh bin nisht gevoynt tsu geyn.

00:28:45.717 --> 00:28:47.249
ikh hob tsu geyn, ikh hob gemeynt

00:28:47.249 --> 00:28:49.355
m'nemt a shnorer oyf shabes?

00:28:49.952 --> 00:28:53.979
undz gey'mir nisht oyf shabes in ergets nisht, undz e'mir zayn in der heym." zog ikh, vos vet ir esn?

00:28:54.660 --> 00:28:58.181
undz ho'mir gehat nokh fun der heym, fun Italye gebrengt,

00:28:58.238 --> 00:29:01.185
ho'mir gehat farshidene fish, konzerves,

00:29:02.052 --> 00:29:03.581
mir ho'mir fun dort gebrengt

00:29:03.638 --> 00:29:09.420
deye ROLLS un azelkhe vi khales ho'mir gehat, zog ikh, "undz ho'mir

00:29:09.780 --> 00:29:14.145
az ir vilt kent ir undz brengen milkh a bisl, undz e'mir."

00:29:16.378 --> 00:29:20.118
dort iz gevezn in in a fridzhider iz gevezn vaser,

00:29:22.960 --> 00:29:27.015
un zey zenen avekgegangen,

00:29:27.015 --> 00:29:30.227
un gekumen shpeter mit mit a a halbe sho,

00:29:30.537 --> 00:29:33.925
un zey hobn gebrengt tsholnt,

00:29:33.925 --> 00:29:37.655
s'geven m'hot gemakht a blekh, aroyfgeleygt zey hobn ongetsundn deys,

00:29:37.655 --> 00:29:39.626
s'dokh heys, s'zumer,

00:29:40.307 --> 00:29:42.261
mir darfn baytn dem TAPE do.

